                            <comment id="17472" author="mehraan" created="Wed, 3 May 2006 12:55:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I used this class instead of org.springframework.transaction.annotation.AnnotationTransactionAttributeSource as the transactionAttributeSource of TransactionProxyFactoryBean and it works fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17604" author="robh" created="Sun, 14 May 2006 14:02:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added BridgeMethodResolver and ReflectionBasedBridgeMethodResolver to cover the resolution of bridge methods. ClassUtils now presents a findBridgedMethod which delegates down to BMR. AnnotationUtils now correctly resolves bridge methods before querying for annotations.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
